            <h1>Learning From Complex Cases</h1>
            <h2>82-Year-Old Male with Recurrent Pneumonia</h2>
            
            <div class="box" style="margin-top: 40px;">
                <h3>Learning Objectives</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Develop systematic approaches to comprehensive chart review</li>
                    <li>Recognize infection risk in chronic lymphoproliferative disorders</li>
                    <li>Apply clinical reasoning when lab and clinical findings diverge</li>
                    <li>Implement antibiotic stewardship principles</li>
                    <li>Identify opportunities for quality improvement</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning-box">
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> Real de-identified case. Focus on learning and systems improvement.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SLIDE 2 -->
        <div class="slide">
            <h1>Initial Presentation</h1>
            
            <div class="box">
                <h3>Chief Complaint</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 1.3em; font-weight: bold;">"Altered mental status, breathing problem"</p>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Timeline</h3>
            <div class="box">
                <p><strong>First Admission (Day -8):</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Neighbor found patient confused, short of breath × several days</li>
                    <li>Unable to provide history (dementia)</li>
                    <li>CXR: Bibasilar opacities</li>
                    <li>Started IV antibiotics, improved</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning-box">
                <p><strong>Day 5:</strong> Left Against Medical Advice</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Had capacity, alert & oriented × 3</li>
                    <li>Family wanted placement, patient refused</li>
                    <li>"Tired of being in hospital"</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="critical-box">
                <p><strong>48 Hours Later:</strong> Re-presentation</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Found somnolent by neighbors</li>
                    <li>SpO2 84% on room air</li>
                    <li>Initially hypotensive (BP 65/45)</li>
                    <li>Transferred to our facility</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>Context:</strong> Lives alone, progressive dementia, medication non-compliance, still driving</p>
        </div>

        <!-- SLIDE 3 -->
        <div class="slide">
            <h1>Laboratory Data (Day 1)</h1>
            
